persons:
    person-the-weeper:
        properties:
            name:
                value: "The Weeper"
            alias:
                - value: "The Weeper"
            gender: male
        notes: "Wildling raider, known enemy of the Night's Watch. Led Mance Rayder's outriders on the Milkwater. Fleshy blond man with watery eyes (the source of his name). Carried a great curved scythe of sharpened steel. Encountered Jon Snow when Rattleshirt brought him to Mance's camp. Like Rattleshirt and Harma Dogshead, a known named raider with a fearsome reputation at the Wall."
